# holospaces V&V absorption (MG-7): the vv/ framework (~250K: suites/lib/heavy/run.sh/
# PROVENANCE.md) is versioned, but the 170M vv/artifacts/ tree is carried EXTERNALLY —
# reproduced/fetched from each artifact's pinned SOURCE.txt by vv/run.sh, verified by
# re-derivation on import, skip-when-absent locally. Never commit the artifacts (repo bloat).
vv/artifacts/

sdk/python/build/
sdk/python/*.egg-info/
sdk/typescript/**/dist/
.superpowers/

# @vscode/test-web downloads a VS Code web build here (CC-17 fetched-by-pin); the browser
# suites mutate it — never track it.
spaces/holospaces-browser/web/.vscode-test-web/

# holospaces docs V&V (Phase G): install-tools.sh materializes ~1.6G of tools here (Structurizr.war,
# cmark-gfm, pandoc, playwright); the 7 source pins (tools/*.txt|*.ebnf|*.rb) stay tracked. The
# arc42-generator vendor tree + the generated build/ are never committed.
specs/holospaces/tools/bin/
specs/holospaces/tools/cmark-gfm-src/
specs/holospaces/tools/cmark-prefix/
specs/holospaces/tools/pandoc-*.deb
specs/holospaces/tools/pandoc-prefix/
specs/holospaces/tools/playwright-browsers/
specs/holospaces/tools/structurizr.war
specs/holospaces/build/
*.redb
